{"tid":1048830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遛狗無牽繩　毛孩遭3車連環撞　主人目擊嚎哭","createTime":"2019-03-06T01:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T04:02:28.000Z","uid":225464,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"04ad6911e5805576e4c3a6052e36deac85007eb6","tid":1048830,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:03:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>遛狗無牽繩 毛孩遭3車連環撞 主人目擊嚎哭</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2EP5ARp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EP5ARp&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=605b9f43\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2EP5ARp</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/photo/bkn-20190306081531737-0306_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190306085729\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190306%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190306081531737-0306_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190306085729&h=c8a0a059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狗狗，安息！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遛狗時應繫好狗帶，拖實愛犬。近日有狗狗慘被三車連環撞斃，主人當場淚崩。路經現場的電影《毛俠》女演員安采妮幫忙救狗，又勸告各位狗主一定要拖繩。<br />\n<br />\n以動物保護為題材的電影《毛俠》監製陳達仁星期一（4日）在其Facebook上傳影片，指有狗主帶狗狗散步時，沒有繫上狗帶，最終狗狗遭三車撞倒，當場爆肚動彈不得。<br />\n<br />\n演員安采妮剛巧路經，與一旁的途人合力將狗狗送往附近獸醫診所。女狗主難掩悲痛，在愛犬身旁不斷哭叫︰「Lucky醒呀！Lucky！」可惜狗狗最終返魂乏術。<br />\n<br />\n滿身狗狗鮮血的安采妮傷感地道︰「真係再奉勸各位，出街一定要拖繩，你以為隻狗好叻，可以跟住你，但其實唔係呀&hellip;一個生命就咁走咗」。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛痛心指︰「意外嘅嘢，一次都多，狗狗安息」、「一條繩，一條命」、「唔拖繩永遠最無辜都係毛小孩」、「隻狗幾乖都有好奇心，拖繩係主人嘅責任」。"},{"pid":"60901da4df31d8514dc3e4fc198f65116e1e1b3b","tid":1048830,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/photo/bkn-20190306081531737-0306_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190306085729\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190306%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190306081531737-0306_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190306085729&h=90be0971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安采妮與熱心男途人把狗狗送往獸醫診所。圖左為女狗主。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"03c3287fdf0e4228483168804c9fa4ae8701725b","tid":1048830,"uid":29423,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:05:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾狗主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99722e3736699aa603299b39a55d2c64d5b1c71","tid":1048830,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:05:08.000Z","msg":"究竟拖條繩係咪好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a524d9754ab31949e0dc30022ad2647857bafa1","tid":1048830,"uid":75994,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60901da4df31d8514dc3e4fc198f65116e1e1b3b","tid":1048830,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/photo/bkn-20190306081531737-0306_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190306085729\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190306%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190306081531737-0306_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190306085729&h=90be0971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安采妮與熱心男途人把狗狗送往獸醫診所。圖左為女狗主。（互聯網）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:06:27.000Z","msg":"熱心男準備開餐食狗肉同女主人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9390db9bab229e36dbc200dee9d5a91944e7b453","tid":1048830,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:06:46.000Z","msg":"仲有D 過份D 小型狗都唔拖狗繩"},{"pid":"dc5f4c36cc61b0e240e6c11bc9c2d7768e5b22b2","tid":1048830,"uid":218364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:07:38.000Z","msg":"講到點愛毛孩，動保撚都係9upL。"},{"pid":"6110ca0ff0d6d88a53b37e2b59c49a47f12e4ddb","tid":1048830,"uid":52459,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:08:11.000Z","msg":"抵撚死，畜主成撚日覺得自己係小精靈訓練員，由得隻畜生亂跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b569b6f7e52f2573f42202acf095363b6d80c4b7","tid":1048830,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c